，即時與我們的義工在網上交談，或致電我們24小時電話熱線2389-2222，與我們的義工傾訴。<br />\n<br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"cdfa663be3a99b4a8ea8e4265415939ce46540bb","tid":1587152,"uid":271739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:15:20.000Z","msg":"兩年前已停用social media 理由同你差唔多 曾經既我都包裝得好好 睇得太多發覺所有野都好虛偽好機心<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"635d48eb48cb604a8838421133be4ccd621afbc7","tid":1587152,"uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"Social media都可以講唔開心"},{"pid":"7abb93deb361e407e113cda5025924e7c86a0ade","tid":1587152,"uid":175799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"635d48eb48cb604a8838421133be4ccd621afbc7","tid":1587152,"uid":310637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T09:17:14.000Z","msg":"Social media都可以講唔開心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:39:09.000Z","msg":"不過唔會有人理<br />\n好想唔再上但自己忍唔到<br />\n總係幾個鐘睇一次"},{"pid":"d51823446b6b2a15d6c250eba35fb9e054d038a8","tid":1587152,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"因為唔想俾d公司起底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f594cd15324c48a02430efb579547e8513a33913","tid":1587152,"uid":155781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:41:57.000Z","msg":"我會直接Unfollow佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16fcbe4b9be7bce5f6c845f0e89e4e3b17b2d9ac","tid":1587152,"uid":156327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T12:56:22.000Z","msg":"見人成日貼到enjoy life<br />\n又去旅行 又fine dining <br />\n好似唔洗錢咁"},{"pid":"8d0c88c7b1c2875a3fbd81858a7028d0327d91eb","tid":1587152,"uid":79375,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-23T13:02:07.000Z","msg":"認識的人唔post 野，<br />\n得堆無謂個post 食買玩得來沒營養的圖文，<br />\n無聊"},{"pid":"abcfd243494a2f0026060a1513e3ec192c603928","t